<br>
Some Blue Diamond jewelry is trivial at 250, but neither Platinum nor Velium are.  Even a combine that is way-way trivial always has that 5% chance at a failure.  Like Gnarl said, decide what you want/need to be made out of that gem and Ely will be glad to attempt it.  Or you could probably ask Gnarl herself, as *she* has her GM Trophy.<br>
<br>
