<br>
2 x BD bracers<br>
1 x Gold Diamond mask<br>
2 x Velium Diamond rings<br>
2 x BD earrings<br>
<br>
The goal is to get to fire, cold and magic resists of 100+, so if you find that one of your characters has a high resist already you may decide to 'skip' a piece.  <br>
<br>
Yes, this is expensive.  I built up my resist gear slowly as I got the gem drops and money.  I found it invaluable for dragons and also when pulling Hate as a monk, especially since I started pulling Hate quite low.<br>
